The paper discusses a method for expressing and implementing robotics algorithms, which falls under the field of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also addresses issues related to software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in the context of robotics. The proposed approach involves introducing high-level abstractions, which can be seen as a system-level approach to robotics (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the implementation of the approach using different sensors, which could fall under the category of machine learning and robotics (cs.MA).
